data.description: **UPDATE: SELLER WILL CREDIT BUYER $12,000.00 TOWARD RATE BUY-DOWN WITH ASKING PRICE OFFER. First time on the market in nearly 30 years. This 2 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom corner home boast of integrity and the pride of ownership. Exterior of the home demonstrates careful and diligent maintenance (i.e. newer windows, paint and gutters),  while the interior has many possibilities. As you enter do take note of the large entry corridor/hall that opens to the spacious living room area. The large galley kitchen is also quite spacious with plenty of storage, a dining area, and laundry hookups. Step out onto a cozy vinyl covered attached patio/deck to enjoy a low-maintenance backyard with stamped/colored concrete and a fire pit. Property also consisted of two large bedrooms with plenty of closet space and an enclosed office space. Master bedroom is multi-level with a spa tub and additional storage space. Explore your possible ADU potential as this property has a 2-car detached garage.
